[
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Church maintenance update",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Hi, this is Klein Heating and Cooling. Just confirming Thursday morning still works to service the rooftop unit at Bethlehem Lutheran in Aberdeen?",
    "thread_ts": "Church maintenance update",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T11:16:12+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Coffee tomorrow",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Thursday works. South side unit's been running but the fellowship hall hit 78 during my shift yesterday. It's not keeping up.",
    "thread_ts": "Coffee tomorrow",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T11:16:12+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002KLEIN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Appointment reminder",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Got it. We'll check refrigerant levels and the compressor. Has it been struggling all season or did this start recently?",
    "thread_ts": "Appointment reminder",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T11:16:12+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Building committee agenda",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Past couple weeks. Pastor brought it up after Sunday service too. July in South Dakota \u2014 congregation's not sitting through a hot sanctuary, I can tell you that.",
    "thread_ts": "Building committee agenda",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T11:16:12+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002KLEIN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Family visit",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Ha, fair point. What time do you usually get in over there? We'd like to get ahead of the midday heat if we can.",
    "thread_ts": "Family visit",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T11:16:12+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Pharmacy refill",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "I'm in by 7. Earlier the better. Aberdeen's been hitting 90 by noon and that roof gets miserable fast. Already been up there twice this week.",
    "thread_ts": "Pharmacy refill",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T11:16:12+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002KLEIN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Garden plans",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Perfect. We'll have a tech there at 7:30 Thursday. Should be able to diagnose same day. We'll call ahead if anything on our end changes.",
    "thread_ts": "Garden plans",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T11:16:12+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Church maintenance update",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Sounds good. Ask for Gary when you pull up.",
    "thread_ts": "Church maintenance update",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T11:16:12+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002KLEIN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Coffee tomorrow",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Elizabeth, that big Bunn urn in the fellowship hall isn't getting up to temp. Tested it twice this morning. Might want a backup plan before Sunday.",
    "thread_ts": "Coffee tomorrow",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T01:16:28+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Appointment reminder",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Oh no. How bad? Like barely warm or actually cold?",
    "thread_ts": "Appointment reminder",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T01:16:28+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003ELIZAB"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Building committee agenda",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Lukewarm. Takes 45 minutes to hit 160 and it should be running at 190. I can get a part at Runnings if I can figure out which one.",
    "thread_ts": "Building committee agenda",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T01:16:28+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Family visit",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Pastor Mike is NOT going to be happy. Can you tell if it's the heating element?",
    "thread_ts": "Family visit",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T01:16:28+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003ELIZAB"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Pharmacy refill",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Already checked. Pretty sure that's it. Part's maybe $30. I can have it done by Saturday if it comes in.",
    "thread_ts": "Pharmacy refill",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T01:16:28+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Garden plans",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "You're a lifesaver. Should I order it or can you handle that?",
    "thread_ts": "Garden plans",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T01:16:28+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003ELIZAB"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Church maintenance update",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "I'll grab it. Dale at Koffee Kup knows everybody \u2014 I'll ask him tomorrow if Runnings stocks it. If not I'll order online tonight.",
    "thread_ts": "Church maintenance update",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T01:16:28+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Coffee tomorrow",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Perfect. Save your receipt and I'll make sure you get reimbursed. Thank you Gary, seriously \ud83d\ude4f",
    "thread_ts": "Coffee tomorrow",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T01:16:28+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003ELIZAB"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Appointment reminder",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Gary did you end up getting that bulb replaced in the fellowship hall? Pastor Mike's been squinting at the bulletin board all week \ud83d\ude04",
    "thread_ts": "Appointment reminder",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T11:41:16+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Building committee agenda",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Got it yesterday. Had to drag out the tall ladder but it's done. Mike can read his own handwriting now, that's on him.",
    "thread_ts": "Building committee agenda",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T11:41:16+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004RACHEL"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Family visit",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Ha! Fair enough. Hey is Nate coming to help you with the floor wax this Saturday or was that just a rumor",
    "thread_ts": "Family visit",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T11:41:16+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Pharmacy refill",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "He said he would. We'll see. That boy's got a good heart but a loose grip on what time Saturday morning means.",
    "thread_ts": "Pharmacy refill",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T11:41:16+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004RACHEL"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Garden plans",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "\ud83d\ude02 I'll believe it when I see him. You need anything from Runnings before then? I'm heading over Tuesday",
    "thread_ts": "Garden plans",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T11:41:16+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Church maintenance update",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "If they've got that blue shop towel roll, grab me two. I'll pay you back. Dale probably owes me a coffee anyway so it evens out.",
    "thread_ts": "Church maintenance update",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T11:41:16+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004RACHEL"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Coffee tomorrow",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Done. Two rolls. Tell Dale he's off the hook this once \ud83d\ude04",
    "thread_ts": "Coffee tomorrow",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T11:41:16+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Appointment reminder",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Dale doesn't need any encouragement. Man already acts like buying pie counts as generosity.",
    "thread_ts": "Appointment reminder",
    "ts": "2025-12-29T11:41:16+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004RACHEL"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Building committee agenda",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Alex. Ceiling tile came down in the fellowship hall last night. Water damage \u2014 must be from that rain we got Monday.",
    "thread_ts": "Building committee agenda",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T15:05:13+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Family visit",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "How bad is it? Is it the roof or a pipe somewhere?",
    "thread_ts": "Family visit",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T15:05:13+00:00",
    "user_id": "U005ALEXAN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Pharmacy refill",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Roof. Called Randy over at Aberdeen Roofing this morning. Earliest he can get up there is Thursday.",
    "thread_ts": "Pharmacy refill",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T15:05:13+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Garden plans",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "What about the potluck Sunday? Pastor Mike's got 60 people coming through that hall.",
    "thread_ts": "Garden plans",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T15:05:13+00:00",
    "user_id": "U005ALEXAN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Church maintenance update",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "I know. Moved the tables over and set a bucket down. Taped off the wet corner so nobody walks under it. It'll hold.",
    "thread_ts": "Church maintenance update",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T15:05:13+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Coffee tomorrow",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "You want me to come in Wednesday and help rearrange things if it gets worse?",
    "thread_ts": "Coffee tomorrow",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T15:05:13+00:00",
    "user_id": "U005ALEXAN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Appointment reminder",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Wouldn't say no. Pastor Mike's already seen it. He's calm as long as Randy's done before the weekend.",
    "thread_ts": "Appointment reminder",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T15:05:13+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "Building committee agenda",
    "reply_count": "0",
